<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f7f7f7; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: white; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF5A5F, #FF385D); color: white; padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; }
    .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
    .job-card { background: #f7f7f7; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .job-title { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #484848; margin: 0 0 10px; }
    .job-meta { color: #767676; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 14px 28px; background: #FF5A5F; color: white !important; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; margin: 10px 5px; }
    .button-secondary { background: #00A699; }
    .footer { background: #f7f7f7; padding: 30px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #767676; }
    .footer a { color: #00A699; text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>ðŸŽ‰ Job Created Successfully!</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #484848;">Great news! Your job posting has been created and saved as a draft.</p>

      <div class="job-card">
        <h2 class="job-title">{{jobTitle}}</h2>
        <div class="job-meta">
          <p><strong>Company:</strong> {{company}}</p>
          <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{location}}</p>
          <p><strong>Status:</strong> Draft - Ready to publish</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 style="color: #484848; margin-top: 30px;">Next Steps:</h3>
      <ol style="color: #767676; line-height: 1.8;">
        <li>Review your job details</li>
        <li>Select job boards to post to</li>
        <li>Complete payment to publish</li>
      </ol>

      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <a href="{{jobUrl}}" class="button">View Job Details</a>
        <a href="{{editUrl}}" class="button button-secondary">Edit Job</a>
      </div>

      <p style="color: #767676; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px;">
        <strong>Tip:</strong> Jobs posted to multiple boards have 3x higher visibility and receive more qualified applications!
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Â© {{brandName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>
        <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}">Dashboard</a> â€¢
        <a href="{{supportUrl}}">Support</a> â€¢
        <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Unsubscribe</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>